    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
先刻御面<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">遠</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（倒）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>御頼申上候。早速御世話被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>遣難<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>有次第奉<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">二</span>万謝<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">一</span>候。<lb />
然ニ別封桂小五郎先生まで相達申度、何時ニてもよろしく御便の節御送奉<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>願候。<lb />
何卒宜御願申上候。<lb />
<span rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">正月三日<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">拝稽首。</span></span>
<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">梅太郎</span>
<span rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">久保先生</span>
<span rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">左右</span>
<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">才谷梅太郎</span>
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">久保松太郎様　虎皮下<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍</span></span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
